caption.text:
For reals it’s not 😆

If you saw my baby account five months ago you’d have seen the same you are probably going through right now. 

SUPER low views. Like stuck in zero for weeks, to the point I thought that this account was broken 🤣. 

But no it was not. I had one reel going viral and then another one and then it was just a damn cascade effect 🤯. 

Was it strategy? Of course if was, I use the same principle to every piece of content. But was it luck? Of course it was too 🤣. Call it manifesting, connecting with universal intelligence or anything you want.

I told the universe hey boo, I’m tired of showing my face, I don’t want to wash my hair everyday to be in front of a bloody camera when I already spend so much time behind it (I’m a photographer), I have a massive electric bill to pay, I’m tired of painfully growing my other accounts while showing my god given face and I feel so restricted to expressing myself 🤷🏻‍♀️.

I was ready to put in the work and honestly I was decided to post 2-3 reels every day for at least six months until reevaluating this venture. I had seen people making it work with the same structure and I know there was space for me to.👀

And there was! There was space. There were people who did not shy away from my sass and rambling captions. Those were my people! There were more out there like me 🤣. 

And darling, there is space for you too 🖤

If you are starting or thinking of doing so and you are a little discouraged because you feel you might have missed it or because there are so many accounts… so this. Grab another account, yours, your partner, your mum. Someone who’s life is a little different than yours. And check the explore page…

Do you see the same amount of faceless accounts? Or digital marketers? Courses? of course not! 
IG is showing you this because it’s what you are interested in! Not because it’s all there is🖤

So get up, wash your face, clean your shoes and get going. Comment 📌444 so I can tell you how to get started 🖤

Disclaimer: These are my personal results and they are not be typical. They are product of long hours of work, personal and professional experience.

#facelessdigitalmarketingforbeginners
